    "summary": "1–4, Celestial marriage is essential to exaltation in the highest heaven; 5–6, How men are sealed up unto eternal life is explained; 7–8, All spirit is matter.",
    "chapterAugmentations": [],
    "verses": [
      {
        "text": "In the celestial glory there are three heavens or degrees;",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "D&C 76:70. TG Celestial Glory.",
            "start": 7,
            "end": 16
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Heaven. BD Heaven.",
